lead_paragraph: Napoli beat 10-man visitors Carpi 1-0 and Juventus won 2-0 at second-bottom Frosinone on Sunday as the leading pair extended their Serie A winning streaks to move further ahead at the top of the table.

headline.print_headline: Napoli, Juve Runs Continue, Inter Salvage 3-3 Draw
